Proposal for sanction of new Sub-Centres in Mul and Pombhurna Taluks of Chandrapur District
It was under the consideration of the government.
Government Decision: The Government is approving the following new Sub-Centres as "Special Matters" in the Taluks of Mul and Pombhurna of Chandrapur District.
2. Separate action shall be taken by the Zilla Parishad for acquisition of land for the above sub-stations in the prescribed manner and creation of posts after completion of construction.
Government Decision No: Establishment-2024 / P.No.226 / Health-3
